    "description": "If you're a passionate Digital Marketing Manager with drive and ambition, The Man Company in Gurgaon is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout The Man Company:\nThe Man Company is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with The Man Company!",
